      <scopecontent id="aspace_20e04c6823e630532963c775896d3326">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, planning documents, lists, and other materials documenting receptions, dinners, and other social events hosted by the president of Yale University for faculty, alumni, donors, and visitors. Also included are records documenting trips taken by the president and the management of the president's residence.</p>  
